[> Getting started
------------------
1. Install LiteX: https://github.com/enjoy-digital/litex/wiki/Installation

2. Run the simulation:
  ./sim.py (--trace to enable waveform that will be located in build/gateware/dut.vcd)

3. Test on Hardware (Arty A7):
  ./arty.py --uart-baudrate=1000000 --build --load
  lxterm --images=images.json /dev/ttyUSBX --speed=1e6 --no-crc
